internal/kagome
================

This directory contains source files vendored from two upstream projects,
plus a third-party dictionary data file. All three are bundled here (not
fetched via go.mod) so that builds are reproducible and do not depend on
the module proxy.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
kagome — Japanese morphological analyzer
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Files:    tokenizer/, including tokenizer/lattice/ and tokenizer/lattice/mem/
Source:   https://github.com/ikawaha/kagome (v2)
Copyright (c) 2020 ikawaha
License:  MIT (see ./LICENSE)

Files were copied without modification except that import paths referring
to the upstream module have been rewritten to point inside this tree:

    github.com/ikawaha/kagome/v2/tokenizer/...
        -> github.com/digitalbiblesociety/transliterate/internal/kagome/tokenizer/...
    github.com/ikawaha/kagome-dict/dict/...
        -> github.com/digitalbiblesociety/transliterate/internal/kagome/dict/...
    github.com/ikawaha/kagome-dict/ipa
        -> github.com/digitalbiblesociety/transliterate/internal/kagome/ipa

Subcommands (cmd/), examples (_examples/), filters (filter/), documentation
(docs/), test data (testdata/), and *_test.go files were not vendored.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
kagome-dict — dictionary loader and IPA dictionary binding
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Files:    dict/, ipa/dict.go
Source:   https://github.com/ikawaha/kagome-dict
Copyright (c) 2021 ikawaha
License:  MIT (same terms as kagome above)

The builder tool (dict/builder/) and dictionary-build pipeline (ipa/tool/,
uni/tool/) were not vendored — we ship the prebuilt ipa.dict and never
rebuild it.

